data.description:
Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 2.1-bathroom corner townhouse that is move-in ready and filled with upgrades. This immaculate home offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and style.Upon entering, you are greeted by a beautifully upgraded kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, a glass tile backsplash and a multitude of white cabinets providing ample storage space.Throughout the house, enjoy the luxury of updated flooring, creating a modern and low-maintenance living environment.The bathrooms have been tastefully renovated, showcasing a walk-in shower and elegant vanities, elevating the overall aesthetic of the home.This townhouse is equipped with a new hot water heater (2023) and newer A/C system, ensuring optimal comfort and energy efficiency. The large fenced-in patio adds a private outdoor retreat, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying peaceful moments.

Residents of this community are privileged to access fantastic amenities, including a community pool and playground.

The convenience of this location cannot be overstated - with close proximity to I-95, shopping centers, and a variety of restaurants.

Schedule a viewing today and let the next chapter of your life unfold in this move-in ready gem!
